Aumbry
======

.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/pyarmory/aumbry.svg?branch=master
    :target: https://travis-ci.org/pyarmory/aumbry
    :alt: Travis CI Build

.. image:: http://codecov.io/github/pyarmory/aumbry/coverage.svg?branch=master
